<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="примечание" id="примечание">Примечание:</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

Bit set is missing two boolean queries to complement <code><a href="any" class="wikilink1" title="ru:container:bitset:any">any()</a></code> и <code><a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/ru/container/bitset/none" class="wikilink2" title="ru:container:bitset:none" rel="nofollow">none()</a></code>: <code>all()</code> и <code>some()</code>.

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> all: <code>(~bitset).none()</code></div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> some: <code>(~bitset).any()</code></div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
